videos.description: Matthew Moyer gets the dish from Frank Howard and stuffs it home through contact for the Orange.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Moyer gets all the way up for slam

videos.description: Christ Koumadje gets the lob from Braian Angola and finishes with the two-handed slam.
videos.headline: Florida State's Koumadje throws down alley-oop

videos.description: Tyus Battle gets the dish from Frank Howard and drains the 3-pointer for the Orange in the second half.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Battle knocks down 3-pointer

videos.description: PJ Savoy hits a deep 3 for the Seminoles midway through the second half.
videos.headline: Florida State's Savoy drains 3-pointer

videos.description: Tyus Battle attacks the rim and gets the acrobatic layup to drop late in the second half.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Battle goes up-and-under for two

videos.description: Christ Koumadje gets the lob from Braian Angola and slams home the emphatic dunk for the Seminoles.
videos.headline: Florida State's Koumadje throws down thunderous slam

videos.description: Phil Cofer gets a dish from Trent Forest and hits the corner 3 with seconds to go in the second half.
videos.headline: Florida State's Cofer sinks clutch 3

videos.description: Tyus Battle sinks improbable 3-pointer in dramatic fashion to tie the game with 5 seconds to go in regulation.
videos.headline: Syracuse's Battle nails 3 over defenders to send game into OT

videos.description: Phil Cofer sprints the floor and takes it all the way to the rack for two in double overtime.
videos.headline: Florida State's Cofer drops in transition layup
